title: GET_INTERIOR_POSITION
content:
0x77A435B0// GetInteriorPosition
void GET_INTERIOR_POSITION(int interiorId, float* posX, float* posY, float* posZ);Parameters:interiorId: The target interior.posX: posY: posZ: Returns: Interior position.Examples:Lualocal playerPed = PlayerPedId()
local interiorId = GetInteriorFromEntity(playerPed)

if interiorId ~= 0 then
  local x, y, z = GetInteriorPosition(interiorId)
  print("current interior " .. interiorId .. " position is: " .. vec(x, y, z))
end

// GetInteriorPosition
void GET_INTERIOR_POSITION(int interiorId, float* posX, float* posY, float* posZ);

local playerPed = PlayerPedId()
local interiorId = GetInteriorFromEntity(playerPed)

if interiorId ~= 0 then
  local x, y, z = GetInteriorPosition(interiorId)
  print("current interior " .. interiorId .. " position is: " .. vec(x, y, z))
end
